snippet.title: The Penguins of Madagascar™ Video Game Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
The Penguins of Madagascar™ Video Game on Nintendo DSi and DS. 

Available November  2, 2010 

Official Website:
http://www.penguinsofmadagascarvideogame.com

Join Wacky Team Penguin!  The Penguins of Madagascar™ on Nintendo DSi and DS captures the fun of the TV series by bringing the four lovable Penguins together as a team to accomplish their madcap missions in and around the zoo!
